tspan.tspan: Connect to GND pin on Arduino.

text.tspan: THIS SHOWS WIRING FOR A COMMON ANODE LED.
IF YOU ARE USING A COMMON CATHODE LED,
CONNECT THE LONG LEG TO GND INSTEAD OF 5V.

tspan.tspan: EACH INPUT/OUTPUT COMPONENT IS SHOWN SEPARATELY.
WIRES SHOULD BE ADDED TO CONNECT EACH LABELLED
CONNECTION TO THE CORRESPONDING PIN OF THE ARDUINO.

text.tspan: ARDUINO CAN BE POWERED VIA USB CABLE, OR
CONNECT THE POWER JACK CENTER PIN TO GND.
CONNECT POWER JACK SLEEVE TO VIN.
